snippet.title: Diskophoros Alpha Trailer
snippet.description:
Download the free alpha now: https://nmaehlmann.itch.io/diskophoros
Follow me on twitter: https://twitter.com/nmaehlmann


Diskophoros (Greek: "Discus-Bearer") is a fast paced local multiplayer fighting game. Face your friends in thrilling laser disc combat on ever changing procedurally generated maps.
